{"tid":275350,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格：我一日24小時都在忙轉會","createTime":"2017-06-08T03:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T06:15:25.000Z","uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c72df099d91e630f6d0d71095dc298b7fe26f2e","tid":275350,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T03:33:51.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴主教練雲格透露，自從賽季結束以來，他就一直在忙著轉會操作，而有些「私下裡的工作」，是球迷們看不到的。<br />\n<br />\n　　雲格說：「我們每天都在力爭加強球隊的陣容，基本上這要涉及很多看不見的、暗黑的工作（a lot of dark， invisible work）。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「但這就是實情，這也是對我的要求，這意味著我離開辦公室或者上床睡覺都要帶著手機，因為任何事情都可能發生。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「我們每天24小時都保持警覺，為球隊陣容創造出最好的環境。」<br />\n<br />\n　　雲格所說的並不誇張，阿仙奴在事先無徵兆的情況下閃電簽下了史浩克04隊的克拉希納茨，而教授和CEO加斯迪茲正在法國，媒體猜測他們是在追逐里昂前鋒拿卡錫迪。可以說，如果未來某天阿仙奴突然又宣佈了什麼交易，那一定是雲格的「暗黑工作」又有成效了。"},{"pid":"95942e70e9161ee19876b9a3ccdfc70b4e26a43a","tid":275350,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T03:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/114151_2407b3104b52412294e1dc31aede9780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F114151_2407b3104b52412294e1dc31aede9780.jpg&h=127e5296&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2c98d4a3b9924b937922420b5957ab1237e605b","tid":275350,"uid":38321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T03:47:18.000Z","msg":"摩佬：我在放假"},{"pid":"59865b9bab06e6a5b4547c92676b082d9e6c800a","tid":275350,"uid":4609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"下季咪又無前四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2792ec92577bbcb881c879811eccef47adf3c2e9","tid":275350,"uid":17619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:30:57.000Z","msg":"憻抖吧"},{"pid":"9b976a3d5d94a5eb88b6fe1e6dd5c4267219a5a9","tid":275350,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-0